{"books":[{"id":"jfjb","name":"解放军报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"dates":[{"year":1976,"month":2,"day":9}],"page_start":3,"page_end":3,"description":"","is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"title":"教育革命好〔四川清音〕","authors":["杨文全〖HH/换行〗DW：三五三○四部队"],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"东风劲吹红旗飘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万里江山展新貌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"基本路线指方向，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命生产齐飞跃。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"文化革命结硕果，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新生事物涌如潮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天不把别的唱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"单唱教育革命好。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一唱教育革命好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟大领袖发号召。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工人阶级管大学，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开天辟地第一遭。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"教育大权人民掌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红色江山牢又牢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反修防修筑长城，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金光大道路一条。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二唱教育革命好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"德智体育大提高。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阶级斗争为主课，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马列主义指航道。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又红又专干革命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敢想敢干敢创造。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反帝反修显身手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去为人民立功劳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三唱教育革命好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面向工农办学校。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"教育劳动相结合，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三大斗争育新苗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"广阔天地炼红心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"继续革命是英豪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"培养红色接班人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"树大根深基础牢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四唱教育革命好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工农兵中把生招。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大学为咱工农开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工农阔步进学校。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上大学来管大学，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还把学校来改造。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"教育阵地添精兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红日永把征途照。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五唱教育革命好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"修正主义连根刨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么“方向没解决”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么“智育第一条”；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"统统都是怪论调，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚决把它来驳倒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远跟着毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共产主义早来到。"}],"alias":""},"tags":[{"name":"教育革命","type":"主题/事件"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}